After unpacking the tar file; as root:

	Execute the script ./vss-hv-driver-install to build and install
	Hyper-V backup components on a RHEL 5.9 installation. Once the script completes,
	reboot the virtual machine.

	To uninstall Hyper-V backup components, execute the script
	./vss-hv-driver-uninstall. Once the script completes, reboot the virtual machine.
